374
00:32:01,236 --> 00:32:02,820
Vou-me embora.

375
00:33:44,714 --> 00:33:46,174
Caramba!

376
00:33:56,309 --> 00:33:57,894
Pai?

377
00:34:03,274 --> 00:34:05,693
Pai? Estás aí?

378
00:34:06,319 --> 00:34:08,112
